body:
I often play get bored of playing the same champions over and over again, and want to play some other ones that I have skins for to get the skins out for a tumble, but often I forget what skins I actually own.

Would Riot be able to implement a feature (under collections would be fitting) to show ALL of the skins I actually own? I understand you can do this in shops but it does not show legacy skins, and it also shows all the ones you don&#039;t own so you have to scroll through all of them!

